@startuml seq_18_hide_post
title Sequence Diagram: UC-18 Hide Post

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Post Controller" as Controller
participant "Post Service" as Service
participant "Post Repo" as PostRepo
participant "Hide Repo" as HideRepo

User -> Frontend: (1.1) Open a post
User -> Frontend: (2.1) Click "Hide"
Frontend -> Controller: (2.2) POST /api/posts/{id}/hide
Controller -> Service: (3.1) Hide post request
Service -> PostRepo: (3.2) Validate authentication and post visibility
PostRepo --> Service: (3.3) Post is valid

Service -> HideRepo: (4.1) Store hidden-post record
HideRepo --> Service: (4.2) Record created
Service --> Controller: (6.1) Success
Controller --> Frontend: (6.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> User: (5.1/6.3) Remove post from current feed view
@enduml
